summary: HD Basket textures made from the scratch, this is just not scaled up and filtered \"HD\" texture. Also, this is my first mod.
descriptionHtml:
Complete re-texturing for baskets, including normal maps. 

1024 x 2048 resolution compared to vanilla 256 x 512.

***************************************************
NOW WITH 512 x 1024 VERSION TOO!
***************************************************

NO FXAA USED IN SCREENSHOTS.

Just install the files into:
*YOUR SKYRIM FOLDER*/Data/Textures/clutter

This is my first mod for Skyrim, please give _CONSTRUCTIVE_ criticism.

Endorse if you like it, Enjoy!
author: Jimmu aka Himini
